WEBVTT

22:13.960 --> 22:16.310 line:80%
Were you scared that night?

22:17.170 --> 22:18.170 line:80%
If you're afraid,

22:18.200 --> 22:19.280 line:80%
you can tell me.

22:19.480 --> 22:20.660 line:80%
Don't bottle it up.

22:20.830 --> 22:22.000 line:80%
It was nothing.

22:22.000 --> 22:23.150 line:80%
I've seen it all.
